when there are no goats around?

00:11.685 --> 00:14.686
Oh, wait...
Now he's drumming.

00:14.998 --> 00:16.939
Overalls, free coffee refills,
and drumming.

00:17.441 --> 00:20.258
We can stop looking, we found
the world's most annoying hipster.

00:21.090 --> 00:23.261
Max, this isn't a diner
where everything comes

00:23.263 --> 00:24.813
with attitude and E. coli.

00:25.065 --> 00:28.398
This is the cupcake shop.
You own this place.

00:28.485 --> 00:31.818
Ugh, success really
cuts your balls off!

00:36.660 --> 00:38.960
We get it.
Your tribe's in trouble.

00:40.162 --> 00:41.797
Hey, she's kidding.

00:41.799 --> 00:44.299
Just help yourself to a fresh
mocha almond refill.

00:44.301 --> 00:46.835
And by the way, sick beats.

00:48.704 --> 00:50.371
You threw him a peace sign?

00:50.373 --> 00:52.974
What are you, a Japanese teenager?

00:52.976 --> 00:54.843
It's a gesture of goodwill.

00:54.845 --> 00:58.178
Okay, but if I see you doing
an open heart, I will kill you.

00:59.316 --> 01:01.500
