01:21.023 --> 01:23.856
Did you just openly wave
to my ex-boyfriend?

01:24.644 --> 01:26.060
Yeah, I always wave at him.

01:26.062 --> 01:27.278
He didn't die just because

01:27.280 --> 01:29.897
