for his own well-being.

09:10.994 --> 09:14.327
Oh, my God, we are
Rihanna and Chris Brown!

09:14.448 --> 09:16.748
But I'm Chris Brown.

09:17.200 --> 09:20.583
Speaking of Chris Brown,
I'm gonna start to batter.

09:21.621 --> 09:23.138
How's that stove?

09:23.140 --> 09:25.924
