and one time it burned me.

09:28.128 --> 09:30.512
That's why I nicknamed it
"Mom."

09:30.514 --> 09:32.464
What is this wood thing under the leg?

09:32.466 --> 09:34.182
it's the shim.

09:34.184 --> 09:35.984
