10:12.972 --> 10:14.105
Oh, good, you're still here.

10:14.107 --> 10:16.224
Don't anybody leave.
Our night just got worse.

10:16.226 --> 10:19.559
Don't come any closer, super gonorrhea!

10:20.413 --> 10:23.346
I'm sorry to say we lied
to get off our shift.

10:23.350 --> 10:25.484
But we have to bake
1,000 cupcakes by tomorrow,

10:25.486 --> 10:27.986
and our oven broke at the shop,
and we need to use yours.

10:27.988 --> 10:30.288
You lied to me,
and now you want a favor?

10:30.290 --> 10:32.657
Yes. Han, we know
it's a big favor,

10:32.659 --> 10:34.359
and it probably looks
even bigger to you,

10:34.361 --> 10:37.629
but I'm sure you can see past our lie.

10:37.631 --> 10:39.364
And if you can't,
you can get up on that chair,

10:39.366 --> 10:42.417
I could put you on our shoulders...

10:42.419 --> 10:45.637
Long story abnormally short,
will you help us?

10:45.639 --> 10:48.972
Well, those 12 short jokes
really primed me.

10:49.226 --> 10:50.392
Fine, you can use the oven

10:50.394 --> 10:52.043
and any of the supplies you need.

10:52.045 --> 10:54.346
Thank you. We really need
to fill this order.

10:54.348 --> 10:57.148
I'll stay and help.
I also had something to fill,

10:57.150 --> 11:00.483
but I'll just text Sophie
and tell her I'm working.

11:00.904 --> 11:02.487
I'll help too.

11:02.489 --> 11:05.056
I can't bake, but I can sit
and lift the spirits.

11:05.058 --> 11:08.391
