It's open bar, right, Han?

11:09.495 --> 11:11.828
Okay, I'm in too.
Earl, make me a sea breeze,

11:12.199 --> 11:13.915
easy on the breezy.

11:14.517 --> 11:16.067
You know, because of my childhood,

11:16.069 --> 11:17.619
