in ten years and start crying,

11:22.042 --> 11:25.293
this is what it's about.

11:30.869 --> 11:33.119
900 and counting.
Comin' through.

11:33.121 --> 11:34.855
- Where do you want them?
- Put 'em over here,

11:34.857 --> 11:37.824
next to the world's slowest helper.

11:37.826 --> 11:39.559
