to make that one cupcake

11:39.561 --> 11:42.629
than it took James Cameron
to make <i>Avatar.</i>

11:43.481 --> 11:45.964
Well, I been doing this
for two minutes,

11:45.967 --> 11:49.300
and I have to say...
Not for me.

11:50.989 --> 11:53.240
But you know what is for me?

11:53.242 --> 11:56.026
Another free cognac.

