Han, you're off the bag.
I'm moving you to batter.

12:42.357 --> 12:44.240
It's not a demotion, it's just
that you stink at this.

12:44.242 --> 12:45.492
I wanna give you something easier.

12:45.494 --> 12:48.662
Max, you just got that
all over your apron.

12:48.664 --> 12:50.863
I'll wipe it down.
Mine's a mess too.

12:50.865 --> 12:52.365
Ooh, pretty slick move.

12:52.367 --> 12:54.867
You wanna try for my bra next?

12:55.921 --> 12:57.220
Yeah, baby,

12:57.222 --> 13:00.555
