13:01.476 --> 13:04.311
What the hell was that?

13:04.313 --> 13:06.429
What?
It's my guy voice.

13:06.731 --> 13:09.065
That's your go-to
guy voice?

13:09.067 --> 13:12.319
Is his identity being
protected on <i>Dateline?</i>

13:12.321 --> 13:14.938
Well, what's your guy voice like?

